h1. The Apache Karaf Team posted on June 26, 2015\\Karaf 4.0.0 released!

The Karaf team is pleased to announce the availability of [Karaf 4.0.0|index/community/download/karaf-4.0.0-release.html].

 Apache Karaf 4.0.0 is the first production ready version of the new 4.0.0 branch.
 It's a major step forward, including a complete new features resolver, a large set of new features, improvements, and bug fixes.

For more information, please see the [release notes|index/community/download/karaf-4.0.0-release.html].
